  "body": [
    {
      "key": "text",
      "value": {
        "non-repeat": {
          "text": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "Wellcome Collection is bigger, bolder and braver than ever before and many of you have joined us on our curious journey through the development project.",
                "spans": [
                  {
                    "start": 23,
                    "end": 48,
                    "type": "hyperlink",
                    "data": {
                      "link_type": "Web",
                      "url": "https://wellcomecollection.org/visit-us/bigger-bolder-braver"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "We now invite you to be part of our exciting next chapter.",
                "spans": []
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "To celebrate our stunning staircase and spaces old and new, we want to know what the next chapter of your lives hold for you. We’re bigger. We’re bolder. But what ‘‑er’ are you?",
                "spans": []
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "We’ll write your chosen adjective on a colourful ball until 7 May 2015. Soon after, we’ll release the balls loaded with your words down our new staircase in a waterfall of colour.",
                "spans": []
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "Let us know what ‘-er’ you are via Twitter, Facebook or Instagram using the hashtag #Ballsier. Remember to tag us in too! If you’re not on social media, use this online form to submit your adjective.",
                "spans": [
                  {
                    "start": 35,
                    "end": 42,
                    "type": "hyperlink",
                    "data": {
                      "link_type": "Web",
                      "url": "https://twitter.com/ExploreWellcome"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "start": 44,
                    "end": 52,
                    "type": "hyperlink",
                    "data": {
                      "link_type": "Web",
                      "url": "https://www.facebook.com/wellcomecollection/posts/10154091908748538"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "start": 56,
                    "end": 65,
                    "type": "hyperlink",
                    "data": {
                      "link_type": "Web",
                      "url": "https://instagram.com/wellcomecollection/"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "start": 162,
                    "end": 173,
                    "type": "hyperlink",
                    "data": {
                      "link_type": "Web",
                      "url": "https://wellcomecollection.org/what-er-are-you"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "We’ll be tallying up all the responses to share the results after the event, along with photos and a video of the big moment.",
                "spans": []
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "heading2",
              "content": {
                "text": "Part of Bigger, Bolder, Braver",
                "spans": [
                  {
                    "start": 8,
                    "end": 30,
